*   [Feature Learning](/Feature_learning)
*   [Predictive Analytics](/Predictive_analytics) (this includes forecasting, which is just guessing the future with more math)

**Spatial and Flow Analysis:**
*   [Social Network Analysis](/Social_network_analysis) (including predicting links)
*   Mapping
*   [Routing](/Routing)

